askppplt:enum.askppplt:name: NATIVE
askppplt:enum.askppplt:description: NATIVE * the trunk members are filled * according to the order given by application. * Regular trunk may hold max of 8 members. * Cascade trunk may hold : * max of 64 members

askppplt:enum.askppplt:name: FLEX
askppplt:enum.askppplt:description: FLEX * A mode to allows flexibility for * each Regular trunk to state it's max number of members (before starting to add members). * (this mode not effect 'cascade trunk' members) * Regular trunk may hold : max of 4K members. (each trunk set it's own limit) * Cascade trunk may hold : max of 64 members.
